{"tid":987133,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《沙贊》戰袍總造價逾 1000 萬美元　拒絕全 CGI 讓服裝師量身打造！","createTime":"2019-01-19T05:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T06:35:07.000Z","uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f83f72df038a4f4fc700438f3c665200136f1a40","tid":987133,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86757/5c42856b4be13.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86757%2F5c42856b4be13.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=0421549b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在去年底溫子仁首度執導的 DC 超級英雄電影《水行俠》（Aquaman）已經於全球熱賣超過 10.38 億美元之後，接下來就要上演 DC 和漫威兩大「驚奇隊長」之戰！因為英文名稱都是 Captain Marvel，DC 即將於 4 月上映的無厘頭喜劇超級英雄電影已經更名為《沙贊！》（Shazam!），並由身高 191 公分的高壯男演員柴克萊威（Zachary Levi）主演，他過去曾在兩部《雷神索爾》電影中飾演過配角范達爾（Fandral），這位演員還以喜劇影集《宅男特務》（Chuck）的主角角色備受觀眾喜愛，而 DC 也是因此看上了柴克萊威的喜劇魅力，讓他在阿斯嘉毀滅之後趕緊跳槽過來。<br />\n不過事實上喜劇風格的《沙贊！》雖然性格和電影劇情設定完全沒有像超人、蝙蝠俠一樣酷帥有型、身處在土豪家庭或來自於克利普頓星，尤其是《沙贊！》預告曝光之後，許多影迷都笑說他肯定會是 DC 電影史上「最屁孩超級英雄」。但事實上 DC 可沒有因此而怠慢了沙贊這個角色，男主角柴克萊威身上那一件紅色的緊身戰袍，讓我們可以清楚看見他手臂的肌肉線條，電影服裝設計師 Leah Butler 就在《Total Film》雜誌的訪問中透露這部電影所有沙贊戰衣的造價就超過 1000 萬美元。<br />\n雖然《沙贊！》這件盡力模仿還原漫畫中的紅色戰袍，在預告釋出之後被不少網友批評「看起來廉價」，但事實上每一件戰袍都要上百萬美元的成本，而《沙贊！》電影則一共做了 10 套，所以光是男主角的服裝上就花了超過千萬美元。造價會這麼昂貴的原因，除了做成了更能顯現肌肉線條的纖維外衣，這套戰袍還安裝了不少電子設備，像是裝上電池就能夠讓沙贊胸前的 LOGO 隨時發光。<br />\n柴克萊威在製作戲服前就進行了嚴格的健身鍛鍊和節食過程，之後劇組用 3D 列印技術取得柴克萊威全身的線條，花了 16 個星期才做出這套為柴克萊威量身打造的沙贊戰衣，這樣直接打造的衣服將會比整體大量使用 CGI 的特效效果看起來更為真實，《沙贊》將於 2019 年 4 月 3 日搶先在台灣上映。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L8V_ASjcfb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL8V_ASjcfb4&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d93a844c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L8V_ASjcfb4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.juksy.com/archives/86757\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.juksy.com%2Farchives%2F86757&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4afd123b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.juksy.com/archives/86757</a>"},{"pid":"5962541183cef5597dec19f35fc5923175d5a211","tid":987133,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bded4c0fa34b86cf5b49f8f0da9a2eacc278af","tid":987133,"uid":16635,"like":36,"dislike":4,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"呢套睡衣1000萬美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無吹到咁大<br />\n主角片酬都唔知有無1000萬美金<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOYtmtP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOYtmtP.png&h=6be8e42e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff2e4241a0dae69e03aab265a9b6ba84dba44b25","tid":987133,"uid":34123,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3D打印取得全身線條</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5ff5560c9f18c2579f35183b32205d48686c88","tid":987133,"uid":159183,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:37:03.000Z","msg":"套衫真係麻麻地"},{"pid":"bdad21776a9fb68468b1975333550a1ef8a0482d","tid":987133,"uid":57543,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"DC不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf125bef3960b6506e44b683bc85ba2250e30ca4","tid":987133,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Each suit costs, oh boy, upwards of a million? We have ten suits.&quot; &mdash; That quote published in Total Film from Shazam! costume designer Leah Butler has been sparking headlines about the DC superhero movie spending $10 million JUST to make Zachary Levi look heroic. <br />\n<br />\nThat would be an insane allocation for a movie that has a budget in the $80 million to $90 million range.<br />\n<br />\nBut sources tell Heat Vision that $1 million per suit figure is wildly inflated, particularly as the New Line and Warner Bros. film is being billed as a more modestly budgeted kind of superhero pic. In fact, a source says the Shazam suit is more in the $60,000 to $70,000 range. That's about $600,000 for 10 suits, which is still noteworthy.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://link.hollywoodreporter.com/view/5c2a375ebec7c3265d3cf8549dkgy.9zn/ac94714d?utm_source=t.co&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fview%2F5c2a375ebec7c3265d3cf8549dkgy.9zn%2Fac94714d%3Futm_source%3Dt.co%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8a412f00\" target=\"_blank\">https://link.hollywoodreporter.com/view/5c2a375ebec7c3265d3cf8549dkgy.9zn/ac94714d?utm_source=t.co&amp;utm_medium=referral</a><br />\n<br />\n吹大左"},{"pid":"6ec4a51e4cf58567658a3efc96b134abba1ac124","tid":987133,"uid":35656,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"Aquaman收得係因為溫子仁拍得好咋  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3aef512b5ec98f83c48ed2a42b5a2cd1a4dd56","tid":987133,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"同BVS 果時唔知用左幾多錢令superman睇上去冇胡鬚一樣on9"},{"pid":"cb9c83926abaa41594986e32cce1d96863f3afbf","tid":987133,"uid":159183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c3aef512b5ec98f83c48ed2a42b5a2cd1a4dd56","tid":987133,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"同BVS 果時唔知用左幾多錢令superman睇上去冇胡鬚一樣on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"jl呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3ab32df8efa120baad01668e622845f297897d","tid":987133,"uid":159183,"like":